		"description": "<p>You call upon your conviction to produce a minor magical effect. Choose one:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You manifest a visible sign of divine power such as spectral wings, or a halo until the beginning of your next turn.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The sound of your footsteps becomes an ominous, booming tread until the beginning of your next turn.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A melee weapon you are wielding gains the Defensive (any) or Thrown (10/40) property for one minute.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You may shout a single word and be both heard and understood by every creature within 300 feet of your location, regardless of background noise or language barriers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
